Gang, I don't know about this.

278
00:12:11,231 --> 00:12:13,666
It's only a matter of
time before they find us!

279
00:12:13,666 --> 00:12:17,136
Genki, Mocchi, come
back and rescue us.

280
00:12:19,305 --> 00:12:21,374
(grunting)

281
00:12:21,374 --> 00:12:24,644
♪

282
00:12:24,644 --> 00:12:26,779
We've gotta get a lot stronger,

283
00:12:26,779 --> 00:12:29,716
'cause Holly and the
others are counting on us.

284
00:12:29,716 --> 00:12:32,385
♪

285
00:12:32,385 --> 00:12:34,554
Don't stop now.

286
00:12:34,554 --> 00:12:41,728
♪

287
00:12:41,728 --> 00:12:44,030
(panting)

288
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:49,736
♪

289
00:12:49,736 --> 00:12:52,672
You two have worked hard.

290
00:12:52,672 --> 00:12:56,276
We've hardly even started,
and we're exhausted!

291
00:12:56,276 --> 00:12:58,011
It's pathetic.

292
00:12:58,011 --> 00:13:00,747
(panting)

293
00:13:02,348 --> 00:13:05,718
Those eyes, they're
filled with passion.

294
00:13:05,718 --> 00:13:07,754
You're so focused on your goal.

295
00:13:07,754 --> 00:13:09,789
The Tainted Kat Brothers
looked just the same

296
00:13:09,789 --> 00:13:11,524
a very long time ago.

297
00:13:11,524 --> 00:13:15,528
‐The Tainted Kat Brothers?
‐They used to be my disciples.

298
00:13:15,528 --> 00:13:18,331
♪

299
00:13:18,331 --> 00:13:21,267
That was before things changed.

300
00:13:21,267 --> 00:13:24,704
It all started a long time ago.

301
00:13:24,704 --> 00:13:26,806
I was training them hard.

302
00:13:26,806 --> 00:13:28,808
I even had them sit
under a cold waterfall

303
00:13:28,808 --> 00:13:30,276
to toughen them up.

304
00:13:30,276 --> 00:13:33,346
(growling)

305
00:13:33,346 --> 00:13:35,081
I can't take it!

306
00:13:35,081 --> 00:13:37,550
‐I quit!
‐But Brother!

307
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:39,619
Get back under there right now!

308
00:13:39,619 --> 00:13:40,653
No chance!

309
00:13:40,653 --> 00:13:42,722
I became your disciple
to get stronger,

310
00:13:42,722 --> 00:13:46,092
‐not to play water sports!
‐But Brother!

311
00:13:46,092 --> 00:13:48,361
One increases his
strength precisely

312
00:13:48,361 --> 00:13:50,263
by gaining control
over his heart!

313
00:13:50,263 --> 00:13:51,764
Have you forgotten that already?

314
00:13:51,764 --> 00:13:53,766
That's just mumbo jumbo!

315
00:13:53,766 --> 00:13:55,735
I wanna fight
with my bare hands!

316
00:13:55,735 --> 00:13:58,338
‐You wanna what?
‐I'm gonna become strong,

317
00:13:58,338 --> 00:14:01,541
but I'm gonna do it by getting
some real practice fighting!

318
00:14:01,541 --> 00:14:03,276
You're making a mistake.

319
00:14:03,276 --> 00:14:05,011
You'll just destroy yourself!

320
00:14:05,011 --> 00:14:06,245
Let's just see!

321
00:14:06,245 --> 00:14:07,880
I don't need you anymore!

322
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:09,148
Good riddance!

323
00:14:09,148 --> 00:14:10,950
Where are you going?

324
00:14:10,950 --> 00:14:12,452
Wait for me!

325
00:14:12,452 --> 00:14:15,321
You're making a mistake!

326
00:14:15,321 --> 00:14:17,690
And that's how things ended.

327
00:14:17,690 --> 00:14:20,193
♪

328
00:14:20,193 --> 00:14:22,261
‐Wow, that's too bad.
‐'chi.

329
00:14:22,261 --> 00:14:24,731
Forgive me, old people
have a bad habit

330
00:14:24,731 --> 00:14:28,368
of talking about the past.

331
00:14:28,368 --> 00:14:31,371
I can tell you care
about your friends.

332
00:14:31,371 --> 00:14:34,974
They'll always be your friends
as long as you care about them.

333
00:14:34,974 --> 00:14:37,643
You'll get your chance
to prove your friendship.

334
00:14:37,643 --> 00:14:39,812
Remember, you
must never give up.

335
00:14:39,812 --> 00:14:41,180
'chi?

336
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:44,150
And grasp any chance
while you're able to.

337
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,084
‐Hmm.
‐Hmm.

338
00:14:48,354 --> 00:15:00,666
♪

339
00:15:00,666 --> 00:15:02,935
(screaming)

340
00:15:02,935 --> 00:15:05,438
♪

341
00:15:05,438 --> 00:15:08,040
‐Gotcha!
‐Nowhere to run now!

342
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:10,176
Let's see you get
out of this one!

343
00:15:10,176 --> 00:15:12,044
(growling)

344
00:15:12,044 --> 00:15:13,679
Stop right there!

345
00:15:13,679 --> 00:15:16,282
(gasping)

346
00:15:16,282 --> 00:15:17,350
Who's there?

347
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:18,684
Show your face!

348
00:15:18,684 --> 00:15:26,826
♪

349
00:15:26,826 --> 00:15:28,394
Genki!

350
00:15:28,394 --> 00:15:34,167
♪

351
00:15:34,167 --> 00:15:36,502
We're here to rescue
our friends from you two.

352
00:15:36,502 --> 00:15:37,603
'chi!

353
00:15:37,603 --> 00:15:39,639
So, you made it
out of that river.

354
00:15:39,639 --> 00:15:42,308
Ha, this time your
luck won't be so good!

355
00:15:42,308 --> 00:15:45,111
♪

356
00:15:45,111 --> 00:15:47,246
We'll see about that, Kats!

357
00:15:47,246 --> 00:15:49,482
Come and get us,
we're ready for ya!

358
00:15:49,482 --> 00:15:51,317
'chi!

359
00:15:51,317 --> 00:15:53,553
(whimpering)

360
00:15:53,553 --> 00:16:11,337
♪

361
00:16:11,337 --> 00:16:13,439
(laughing)

362
00:16:13,439 --> 00:16:17,343
♪

363
00:16:17,343 --> 00:16:18,878
Mocchi!

364
00:16:18,878 --> 00:16:20,847
Mocchi!

365
00:16:20,847 --> 00:16:23,983
You don't stand a chance
against our whirlwind claws!

366
00:16:23,983 --> 00:16:27,119
♪

367
00:16:27,119 --> 00:16:30,323
Say your goodbyes‐‐ha!

368
00:16:30,323 --> 00:16:32,225
No, they'll be salami!

369
00:16:32,225 --> 00:16:35,161
They'll never win by
just blocking their attacks!

370
00:16:35,161 --> 00:16:36,829
No, you guys!

371
00:16:36,829 --> 00:16:43,336
♪

372
00:16:43,336 --> 00:16:44,570
Look out!

373
00:16:44,570 --> 00:16:46,372
Victory is ours!

374
00:16:46,372 --> 00:16:53,946
♪

375
00:16:53,946 --> 00:16:56,315
(gasping)

376
00:16:56,315 --> 00:16:58,851
♪

377
00:16:58,851 --> 00:17:00,653
Uh‐‐wha‐‐

378
00:17:00,653 --> 00:17:03,389
Cherry blossom blizzard!

379
00:17:03,389 --> 00:17:08,060
♪

380
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:10,229
(yelling)

381
00:17:10,229 --> 00:17:15,568
♪

382
00:17:15,568 --> 00:17:17,203
(growling)

383
00:17:17,203 --> 00:17:20,940
♪

384
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:23,543
‐Hey!
‐You did it!

385
00:17:23,543 --> 00:17:25,344
Are you okay?

386
00:17:25,344 --> 00:17:28,381
You bet, 'cause we learned
a few tricks while we were away.

387
00:17:28,381 --> 00:17:30,449
(laughing)

388
00:17:30,449 --> 00:17:31,584
Huh?

389
00:17:31,584 --> 00:17:35,421
Oh, how could we have lost
to a little kid like that?

390
00:17:35,421 --> 00:17:37,523
♪

391
00:17:37,523 --> 00:17:40,026
‐We lost.
‐It's your fault.

392
00:17:40,026 --> 00:17:44,030
I'll make you pay
for this humiliation!

393
00:17:44,030 --> 00:17:45,097
(gasping)

394
00:17:45,097 --> 00:17:46,132
No!

395
00:17:46,132 --> 00:17:48,901
(growling)

396
00:17:48,901 --> 00:17:50,436
That's enough!

397
00:17:52,204 --> 00:17:53,339
Kato!

398
00:17:53,339 --> 00:17:56,208
‐Master, how‐‐
‐Listen, I'm old,

399
00:17:56,208 --> 00:17:58,978
but I've still got
the right stuff.

400
00:18:00,379 --> 00:18:01,914
You two are brothers.

401
00:18:01,914 --> 00:18:04,517
You shouldn't be
fighting each other.

402
00:18:04,517 --> 00:18:06,552
I know we've had our
problems in the past,

403
00:18:06,552 --> 00:18:08,454
but you'll always
be my disciples,

404
00:18:08,454 --> 00:18:09,989
and you'll always be brothers.

405
00:18:09,989 --> 00:18:11,691
I'm sorry.

406
00:18:11,691 --> 00:18:14,026
(crying)

407
00:18:14,026 --> 00:18:16,796
‐Forgive us, Master.
‐You saved our lives.

408
00:18:16,796 --> 00:18:18,531
How can we repay you?

409
00:18:18,531 --> 00:18:23,235
By making a new start, as
my disciples and as brothers.

410
00:18:23,235 --> 00:18:25,404
‐Thank you, Master.
‐Thank you, Master.

411
00:18:25,404 --> 00:18:28,774
(grunting)

412
00:18:28,774 --> 00:18:29,976
‐Goodbye!
‐See ya!

413
00:18:29,976 --> 00:18:33,980
‐Take care!
‐Bye‐bye, 'chi!

414
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:35,848
‐So long!
‐Sorry!

415
00:18:35,848 --> 00:18:37,850
No hard feelings!

416
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:38,884
‐Bye!
‐See ya!

417
00:18:38,884 --> 00:18:40,019
‐Bye!
‐Bye!

418
00:18:40,019 --> 00:18:41,921
Don't forget to write!

419
00:18:41,921 --> 00:18:44,824
They'll be fine, even
against the Baddies.

420
00:18:44,824 --> 00:18:47,393
As long as the three
of them stick together.

421
00:18:47,393 --> 00:18:50,162
It's such a big relief that
everyone made it out okay.

422
00:18:50,162 --> 00:18:52,264
Except my stomach!

423
00:18:52,264 --> 00:18:54,800
Yeah, Genki, Suezo's right.

424
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:57,103
Golem still hungry!

425
00:18:57,103 --> 00:18:59,772
Oh, that's right, we
still haven't eaten!

426
00:18:59,772 --> 00:19:02,208
So how about we celebrate
with a big feast?

427
00:19:02,208 --> 00:19:04,510
‐Yeah!
‐Let's eat!

428
00:19:04,510 --> 00:19:24,997
♪

429
00:19:24,997 --> 00:19:26,699
So this is it, huh?

430
00:19:26,699 --> 00:19:28,734
The machine that
will allow Master Moo

431
00:19:28,734 --> 00:19:30,369
to merge with his body?

432
00:19:30,369 --> 00:19:31,904
Yeah, I'm sure of it!

433
00:19:31,904 --> 00:19:33,606
This is the big one!

434
00:19:33,606 --> 00:19:36,776
We finished the wiring
on the final gate!

435
00:19:36,776 --> 00:19:39,478
‐Right, then we'll depart.
‐Yes, sir!

436
00:19:39,478 --> 00:19:44,817
♪

437
00:19:44,817 --> 00:19:46,919
(squeaking)

438
00:19:46,919 --> 00:19:49,588
(whizzing)

439
00:19:49,588 --> 00:20:11,610
♪

440
00:20:11,610 --> 00:20:13,179
The final gate.

441
00:20:13,179 --> 00:20:15,214
They finally found it.

442
00:20:15,214 --> 00:20:24,156
♪

443
00:20:24,156 --> 00:20:28,094
I can't believe it's actually
come to this, Big Blue.

444
00:20:28,094 --> 00:20:31,097
We're running out of time,
so let's get a move on.

445
00:20:31,097 --> 00:20:32,765
Right.

446
00:20:32,765 --> 00:20:37,169
♪

447
00:20:37,169 --> 00:20:39,038
(thudding)

448
00:20:39,038 --> 00:20:47,146
♪

449
00:20:47,146 --> 00:20:48,347
♪ Monsters ♪

450
00:20:48,347 --> 00:20:49,982
♪ Monsters rule ♪

451
00:20:49,982 --> 00:21:14,507
♪

452
00:21:14,507 --> 00:21:15,975
♪ Monsters rule ♪

